      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 108,
      "message": "rename to 'jsonDataWithSpacesInArrayElement' for clarity\nand move this into the the 'when' block ie. just before line 122\n\nactually there are 2 alterantives whatever you prefer:\n\nA)\ngiven: 'schema context'\n\n            def yangResourcesMap = TestUtils.getYangResourcesAsMap('bookstore.yang')\n            def schemaContext = YangTextSchemaSourceSetBuilder.of(yangResourcesMap).getSchemaContext()\n        when: 'json array element having space is parsed'\n            def jsonDataWithSpacesInArrayElement = org.onap.cps.TestUtils.getResourceFileContent('bookstore.json')\n            def result = YangUtils.parseJsonData(jsonDataWithSpacesInArrayElement, schemaContext)\nB)\ngiven: 'schema context'\n\n            def yangResourcesMap = TestUtils.getYangResourcesAsMap('bookstore.yang')\n            def schemaContext = YangTextSchemaSourceSetBuilder.of(yangResourcesMap).getSchemaContext()\n        and : 'some json data with space in teh array elements'\n            def jsonDataWithSpacesInArrayElement = TestUtils.getResourceFileContent('bookstore.json')\n        when: 'that json data is parsed'\n            def result = YangUtils.parseJsonData(jsonDataWithSpacesInArrayElement, schemaContext)\nB is probably better",
