    {
      "id": "4b147f35_e67f90a5",
      "file_path": "cps-rest/src/test/groovy/org/onap/cps/rest/controller/DataRestControllerSpec.groovy",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 67,
      "message": "Yes I also agree with Renu it's valid point. I investigated further and found there was problem with jsonObject = groovy.json.JsonOutput.toJson(jsonString); that produces output with \"{\"some-key\". I modified unit test to except  jsonString into content body of request using .content(jsonString) and removed groovy.json.JsonOutput.toJson(jsonString) as it's not required any more.",
